name: Migraine
title: Migraine
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to migraine.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes migraine terms in relation to intractable/not intractable, aura, hemiplegic, unspecified, other, and persistent migraines.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes migraine terms in relation to cyclical vomiting syndrome, cerebral infarction, menstruation, optical, abdominal, and chronicity.)
